WEBVTT

00:00:26.830 --> 00:00:28.380
Yggdrasil...

00:00:29.550 --> 00:00:30.840
There's no mistaking it.

00:00:30.840 --> 00:00:32.630
This is Alne,

00:00:32.630 --> 00:00:36.470
the center of Alfheim and the largest city in this world!

00:00:36.470 --> 00:00:39.180
Yeah. We finally made it, huh?

00:00:39.430 --> 00:00:43.310
It's my first time coming to such a massive city.

00:00:43.310 --> 00:00:44.980
Me too.

00:00:44.980 --> 00:00:49.110
The lights of the mineral towers look like stardust.

